# =====================================================
# HISTORY & CONTEXT — KEPT IN GIT ON PURPOSE
# =====================================================
# This repo is designed to give persistent, rich context to Grok
# via public raw files. We WANT to track evolution of usage,
# past conversations, decisions, and old prompt versions.
#
# Do NOT ignore these:
# conversations/   - captured rich conversations
# decisions/       - important decisions and reasoning
# deprecated/      - old prompt/context versions (historical)
# legacy/          - previous full snapshots or big refactors
# logs/            - activity logs showing patterns over time
#
# When starting "novo fluxo de conversação", we reset/copy clean
# base placeholders instead of deleting history.
#
# If something specific becomes too noisy later, move it to legacy/
# or ignore explicitly with clear commit message.
